The paper deals with image matching and geopositioning, which are primarily computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) topics. The use of convolutional features and clustering algorithms also suggests a possible fit with multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the use of outlier removal and coordinate estimation algorithms suggests a possible fit with machine learning (cs.LG) as well.
